    "description": "<i><br>                                                                          白天的森林宁静祥和。<br>                                                                          而当夜幕降临，你就会听到吼叫声……<br>                                                                                                    ……那是怪兽在嘶吼。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/0007342629d9840e1d2e891cec49a83f.avif?t=1728985491\" width=630 height=122 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/f634b67b04eb768aea892b2789d6624f.webp?t=1728985491\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br>本游戏由《Little Briar Rose》创作团队与Luna2工作室合力打造，玩家将进入美丽而恐怖的手绘世界，与露西和她的朋友们一起冒险。<br><br>露西害怕森林，就和其他小孩一样：每天夜里，回荡的吼叫声让她难以入睡。即使是在梦里，她也无法安全地肆意玩耍。<br><br>人口失踪在村子里并不稀奇，但这一次，露西已经长到可以独自调查的年纪了。或者说，她是这么认为的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/d5b866d5a318732a25e17d44b57395fa.avif?t=1728985491\" width=630 height=122 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/f634b67b04eb768aea892b2789d6624f.webp?t=1728985491\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br>《<strong>寂静村的孩子们</strong>》是一款指向点击型冒险游戏，讲述一个神秘而动人的故事。探索村子及其危险的周遭区域，遇见生活在其中的古怪生灵，破解各种各样的谜题，掌握精彩有趣的小游戏。<br><br>陪露西一起踏上冒险之旅，调查寂静村怪事频发背后的真相……只要你有胆量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/b09f2a29f19092fa5a7cf315fd2abe7f.poster.avif?t=1728985491\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/b09f2a29f19092fa5a7cf315fd2abe7f.webm?t=1728985491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/b09f2a29f19092fa5a7cf315fd2abe7f.mp4?t=1728985491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 探索寂静村，搜查线索，但注意：<strong>不要到森林里去。</strong><br></li><li> 摄人心魄的独特2D画风，搭配暗黑色彩的神秘故事情节。<br></li><li> 音乐的作用至关重要，学会唱歌可以在需要时帮助露西。<br></li><li> 组合物品可以获得完全出乎意料的效果！ <br></li><li> 众多稀奇古怪的角色（还有动物！）可以进行互动。在他们消失前与之好好相处。<br></li><li> 与村子里其他孩子一起玩小游戏！<br></li><li> 一只特别调皮的猫，设定成一有机会就给露西捣乱。<br></li><li> 离奇的原创谜题：<span class=\"bb_spoiler\">使用一根皮带和一把大剪刀闯入你母亲最好朋友的房子里，准备好去偷……一朵花？！</span></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/69ee6c319663e3948b70f3c17141e9d6.poster.avif?t=1728985491\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/69ee6c319663e3948b70f3c17141e9d6.webm?t=1728985491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108000/extras/69ee6c319663e3948b70f3c17141e9d6.mp4?t=1728985491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
